OL,3,CWelsh Liberal Democrats unveil full
OL,4,CSenedd Election manifesto
OL,6,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrats have
OL,7,Funveiled their manifesto for the
OL,8,FSenedd Election with a firm promise
OL,9,Fnot support 'a penny' being spent on
OL,10,FWelsh independence.
OL,12,FAddressing members in Cardiff,
OL,13,FleaderJane Dodds put forward her case
OL,14,Ffor voters to choose her party when
OL,15,Fcasting her votes next month.
OL,17,FAmong her key pledges - an investment
OL,18,Fof #300m in social care, alongside
OL,19,Ffurther childcare support with fully
OL,20,Ffunded places from nine months old for
OL,21,F30 hours a week for 48 weeks per year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
