OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776359147
OL,3,CWelsh Liberal Democrats unveil full
OL,4,CSenedd Election manifesto
OL,6,FIn her speech to delegates, she also
OL,7,Fpromised to get tough with water
OL,8,Fcompanies by banning bonuses for
OL,9,Fbosses unless sewage discharges into
OL,10,Fwaterways stop.
OL,12,FAs the single Liberal Democrat elected
OL,13,Fin 2021, a recent ITV Wales poll
OL,14,Fpredicted the party will be wiped out
OL,15,Fin the Senedd after May 7th.
OL,17,FUntil now she has been influential in
OL,18,Fpassing budgets in return for
OL,19,Fconcessions such as money for
OL,20,Fchildcare, and a ban on greyhound
OL,21,Fracing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
