OL,3,CWelsh Liberal Democrats unveil full
OL,4,CSenedd Election manifesto
OL,6,FWhen pressed on which parties she
OL,7,Fwould work with as the next Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment she had previously ruled
OL,9,Fout Reform.
OL,11,FShe has also said she would not
OL,12,Fsupport any money being spent on
OL,13,Findependence.
OL,15,FWith Plaid Cymru the other favourite
OL,16,Fin the polls, who have said they would
OL,17,Fspend #500,000 on proposals for
OL,18,Findependence, ITV News pressed her
OL,19,Fwhether this meant she was talking
OL,20,Fherself out of having any prospect of
OL,21,Fhaving any influence in the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
