CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776359147
OL,3,CWelsh Liberal Democrats unveil full
OL,4,CSenedd Election manifesto
OL,6,FShe confirmed the independence
OL,7,Fspending was still a red line for her
OL,8,Fand would not work with Plaid if it
OL,9,Fwas still part of their plans.
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru responded to her speech
OL,12,Fsaying,
OL,14,F"Despite criticising Reform UK for
OL,15,Ftheir plans to privatise the NHS, Jane
OL,16,FDodds has today refused to rule out
OL,17,Fsupporting a Reform UK First Minister
OL,18,Fover a progressive Plaid Cymru one"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
