OL,3,CWelsh Liberal Democrats unveil full
OL,4,CSenedd Election manifesto
OL,6,FWelsh Labour said, "If the people of
OL,7,FWales want to truly stop independence,
OL,8,Fand to stop divisive nationalism
OL,9,Ftaking root here in Wales, the only
OL,10,Fway to do that is to vote Welsh
OL,11,FLabour."
OL,13,FReform leader Dan Thomas said, "The
OL,14,FLib Dems, just like Plaid, have played
OL,15,Fa key role in propping up Labour in
OL,16,Fthe Senedd.
OL,18,FOnly Reform can deliver a fresh start
OL,19,Ffor Wales."
